<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <span class="eyebrow">AI + IoT POS for restaurants</span>
                    <h1>Voice-led ordering that delights guests and boosts throughput</h1>
                    <p>Empower staff and guests to place orders by voice, route items instantly to kitchen stations, and surface AI-powered upsells — built for fast-paced restaurant operations.</p>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Join the pilot program</a>
                        <a href="/pos-software" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Explore the platform</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-meta">
                        <span>Founders-led onboarding</span>
                        <span>Pilot slots for 5 early restaurants</span>
                        <span>Hardware ready for 2025 rollout</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </section>

        <%- include('partials/trust') %>

        <%- include('partials/ecosystem') %>

        <section class="resources">
            <div class="container">
                <span class="eyebrow">Resources</span>
                <h2>Plan your POS rollout with Bhojan Mitra</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Dive deeper into our software, hardware, pricing, and enablement resources — all tuned for restaurants searching for the best POS fit.</p>
                <div class="resources-grid">
                    <article class="resource-card">
                        <h3><a href="/pos-software">AI POS Software</a></h3>
                        <p>See how our voice-first POS software speeds up order capture and analytics for restaurant teams.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="resource-card">
                        <h3><a href="/pos-machine">POS Machine</a></h3>
                        <p>Explore the Bhojan Mitra POS machine, hardware roadmap, and pilot credits for founding partners.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="resource-card">
                        <h3><a href="/pricing">Pricing &amp; Plans</a></h3>
                        <p>Compare founding partner plans, lifetime discounts, and hardware credits available during the pilot.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="resource-card">
                        <h3><a href="/support">Support &amp; Training</a></h3>
                        <p>Learn about founders-led support, training tracks, and how we keep your service running flawlessly.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="features">
            <div class="container">
                <span class="eyebrow">Capabilities</span>
                <h2>Why restaurants choose Bhojan Mitra</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to run a modern dining floor: conversational ordering, real-time routing, and analytics that spot revenue opportunities in seconds.</p>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Voice Ordering</h3>
                        <p>Conversational ordering tuned for restaurant lingo, modifiers, and mixed-language requests.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>AI Recommendations</h3>
                        <p>Boost ticket sizes with intelligent upsells that learn from past orders, inventory, and guest profiles.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>IoT Kitchen Routing</h3>
                        <p>Send tickets to the right kitchen station or device instantly, with prep instructions highlighted automatically.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Analytics &amp; Insights</h3>
                        <p>Get live dashboards, menu performance, and staffing insights without waiting for end-of-day reports.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <%- include('partials/metrics') %>

        <section class="faq-section" id="faq">
            <div class="container">
                <span class="eyebrow">FAQs</span>
                <h2>POS questions operators ask us most</h2>
                <div class="faq-grid">
                    <article class="faq-item">
                        <h3>What makes Bhojan Mitra different from other POS systems?</h3>
                        <p>Bhojan Mitra is voice-first. Orders can be spoken in multiple Indian languages, modifiers are captured automatically, and IoT routing sends tickets to the right kitchen station without manual steps.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="faq-item">
                        <h3>Can Bhojan Mitra replace my existing POS machine?</h3>
                        <p>Yes. We provide a browser-based POS, dedicated hardware, and integrations to your existing printers and displays. During the pilot we map your current workflow and ensure continuity.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="faq-item">
                        <h3>How long does pilot onboarding take?</h3>
                        <p>Most restaurants go live within four weeks. Week one focuses on configuration, week two on training, and weeks three-four on shadow runs before the full switch.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="faq-item">
                        <h3>Does the POS work if the internet drops?</h3>
                        <p>Yes. Bhojan Mitra buffers voice transcripts locally and syncs once connectivity returns. Kitchen routing rules remain active so orders continue to print.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-actions center" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
                    <a href="/pos-machine" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore the POS machine</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Ask a question</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="products">
            <div class="container">
                <span class="eyebrow">Founding plans</span>
                <h2>Reserve your Bhojan Mitra bundle early</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Founding partners receive lifetime discounts, roadmap input, and white-glove onboarding while we move from pilot to full release.</p>
                <div class="products-grid">
                    <div class="product-card">
                        <h3>Simple Billing (Starter)</h3>
                        <p class="price">₹250 / month</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Core billing &amp; invoicing</li>
                            <li>Order capture (manual &amp; QR)</li>
                            <li>Cloud backups &amp; updates</li>
                            <li>Email support</li>
                            <li>Founding partner discount locked for life</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Reserve ₹250 Plan</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-card featured">
                        <h3>Analytics + QR Ordering</h3>
                        <p class="price">₹500 / month</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Advanced sales &amp; staff analytics</li>
                            <li>QR-based customer ordering flow</li>
                            <li>Live dashboards &amp; custom reports</li>
                            <li>Priority email support</li>
                            <li>Roadmap workshops with our team</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Reserve ₹500 Plan</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-card">
                        <h3>Voice-enabled Ordering (Bhojan Mitra)</h3>
                        <p class="price">₹5,000</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Full AI voice ordering (multilingual)</li>
                            <li>IoT kitchen routing &amp; automation</li>
                            <li>Priority onboarding &amp; training</li>
                            <li>Dedicated support</li>
                            <li>Hardware credits for pilot partners</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Reserve Bhojan Mitra</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>See Bhojan Mitra in action</h2>
                <p>Join the pilot to experience voice ordering, IoT routing, and analytics tailored to your restaurant before our public launch.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions center">
                    <a href="https://billing.aarohitavigyan.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply for the pilot</a>
                    <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">View founding plans</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
